---
description: Use the economics-paper-reviewer protocol for English economics paper pre-review.
alwaysApply: false
---

When reviewing an English economics paper, read `AGENTS.md` and `SKILL.md`, then use the canonical protocol in `references/`.

When scores, benchmarking, validation, or human-reviewer comparison are requested, load `references/scorecard.md` through the canonical protocol.

Do not duplicate the protocol here. Keep review outputs evidence-grounded and mark missing evidence as provisional.
